                <h1>Top Colors for Impactful PowerPoint Presentations</h1>
                <p>The best colors for PowerPoint presentations combine clarity with visual appeal. Opt for a palette that includes soft backgrounds like light gray or blue, complemented by vibrant accent colors such as orange or green for text and images. Ensure high contrast between text and background for readability, and stick to 2-3 main colors to maintain consistency.</p>
